snippet.title: Rival Stars Horse Racing: Desktop Edition [PC] Coming Soon Trailer
snippet.description:
Rival Stars Horse Racing is a horse racing management experience where you care for and train your own stable of horses, breed the perfect champion, manage a homestead ranch, and race for victory!


More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/13832/



Rival Stars Horse Racing is expected to launch for PC (Steam) on June 25, 2020.


#RivalStarsHorseRacing #videogames #WorthPlaying #WorthPlayingvideos
